metadata.name: Mint Pass #1
metadata.description:
This is a collection of Mint Pass for Sonic Frontiers NFT - combination of blockchain and platform game.  
Sonic Frontiers NFT holders will get the Digital Deluxe Edition.  
Mint Pass holders can burn their Mint Pass and get Dragon Age NFT for free.  
Visit Site and mint free with Mint Pass; start the journey to uncover the mysteries of the remains of an ancient civilization.
